LAMP - Linux Apache MYsql PHP (Two Tier Architecture)

Prerequesits - ec2 server , Db server , Dns name , ssl certificate 

Steps To be Done:-
==================
1. Create Two Security Groups in AWS - For App & DB Servers
2. Create Two Instances - App & DB
3. Configure App Server
4. Configure DB Server
5. Install ITOP Tool in App server
6. Configure SSL in App Server - Install Certificate
7. Configure DNS in DNS Control Panel
